title: BRIEF-Tenneco Will Pay $200 Mln To Icahn Enterprises' American Entertainment Properties If Deal Terminates Under Some Circumstances
text:
April 10, 2018 / 12:27 PM / Updated 6 minutes ago BRIEF-Tenneco Will Pay $200 Mln To Icahn Enterprises' American Entertainment Properties If Deal Terminates Under Some Circumstances Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 10 (Reuters) - Tenneco : 
* WILL PAY TERMINATION FEE OF $200 MILLION TO ICAHN ENTERPRISES' AMERICAN ENTERTAINMENT PROPERTIES IF DEAL TERMINATES UNDER SOME CIRCUMSTANCES Source text: ( bit.ly/2qj3z8l ) Further company coverage:
